post0.title: Hands on ML Made Easy course on YouTube
post0.content: Note: This post is for beginners who want to learn Machine Learning through python coding and for those who want a structured video lectures of the book, Hands-On Machine Learning with Scikit-learn, Keras and TensorFlow.
